<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Autorizar Sorteio</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body class="bg-light d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center gap-4" style="min-height: 100vh;">
  <a href="/" class="btn btn-danger position-fixed top-0 end-0 m-4">Sair</a>

  <header>
    <h1>Autorizar Sorteio</h1>
  </header>

  <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
    <p class="text-danger">DICA: </p>
    <p class="text-success"> A palavra passe é ITACADEMY, tudo em maiúsculo.</p> 
  </div>

  <section class="container text-center mb-4 d-flex flex-row justify-content-evenly align-items-center">
    <form action="/autorizar-sorteio" method="post">
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label for="codigoAutorizacao" class="form-label">Código de Autorização</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="codigoAutorizacao" name="codigoAutorizacao" required>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger">Confirmar</button>
    </form>
  </section>
  

  <footer class="bg-secondary fixed-bottom py-2 d-flex justify-content-between">
    <p class="text-light" style="padding-left: 1em;">Esse projeto foi criado por Gabriella Müller Borges</p>
    <p class="text-light" style="padding-right: 1em;">Veja mais dos meus projetos <a href="https://github.com/GabriellaMullerBorges" class="text-info">aqui</a></p>
  </footer>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>
